description.spider_armor.name: 穿上蜘蛛鎧甲如同變成蜘蛛。 全套裝備可以讓你攀爬牆壁並且跳得更高。
description.spider_sword.name: 毒液從尖牙中流出，使這把看似簡單的劍成為英雄之刃，一旦你的敵人被這把劍咬住，巨蛛屍羅的毒液就不停的噴湧。
description.bull_armor.name: 穿上公牛鎧甲如同變成公牛， 全套裝備可以讓你擁有更快的衝刺速度， 並且摧毀途徑的一切。
description.great_sword.name: 按住游標右鍵可施展大範圍攻擊，
description.turtle_armor.name: 巨龜的力量，如果你用它的殼做一套完整的裝備並穿上，會讓你更快地恢復生命值。背殼還可以防止從後部造成的大部分傷害。
description.slime_armor.name: 當一整套的史萊姆裝甲接觸到你的外觀時，你會感覺到你最大的生命值在溢出，當你受到傷害時，可能會出現一個小的史萊姆，如果你能接觸到它，它可以恢復你的生命值。
description.cloud_boots.name: 那些踏上天使之歌的先知說，他們從不犯錯。輕輕一躍便能飛升，輕快地行走便打破了聲音的速度， 任何失敗都無法阻止被選中的人， 而當你有了這雙靴子, 你也不例外。
description.dagger.name: 移動時按下游標右鍵以向前跳躍。
description.ninja_dagger.name: 移動時按下游標右鍵以向前跳躍。 據說使用這把匕首的人可以來無影去無蹤。 你也許可以用潛行以及游標右鍵來模仿這種行為，但是注意，當你消失在別人的視野中時，你並沒有移動多遠。
description.bull_battle_axe.name: 右擊地面製造地震
description.walker_set.name: 傳說任何向深淵漫步者之王射箭的人都會突然發現在他們背後多了一把劍，而王就在他們背後。也許得到他的劍和他的盾可以讓你擁有同樣的能力？
description.gun.name: 右鍵發射，需要子彈。
description.bullet_damage.name: 子彈傷害
description.bullet_fire.name: 擊中後點燃目標
description.fire_rate.name: 射速
description.accuracy.name: 精準度
description.click_shift.name: 按住shift鍵查看說明
description.rear_damage.name: 背刺傷害
description.charging.name: 充能中...
description.turtle_armor_charging.name: 冷卻能力，剩餘時間：
description.healing_potion.name: 喝下可以恢復2顆心
description.teleport_stone.name: 古代民族創造的神秘物體。按住右鍵點擊以設定位置，然後再次執行此操作以傳送到該位置。潛行並按住游標右鍵點擊以刪除保存的位置。
description.teleport_stone_position.name: 目前位置：
description.staff_fire.name: 火焰吞噬了那些穿過你的道路的人，只需簡單的右擊，讓他們感受你的怒火吧！順便也點燃火把。
description.staff_spider.name: 右擊發射你的黏稠物質，（←_← ） 伙伴。。。
description.staff_gun.name: 這是一把插在棍子上的槍。哦朋友，那些小矮人真是個天才！
description.staff_healing.name: 左鍵點擊可以恢復你所需要的生命值，我不記得這是怎麼回事，但我出於好玩不得不對所有這些進行描述。
description.contains.name: 包含：
description.empty.name: 空的
description.soul_bottle.name: 左鍵點擊一個怪物來儲存它，右鍵點擊來召喚那個怪物。也可以變成這個怪物的生怪籠。
description.flamethrower.name: Undertech原型Fyrebird MK7 22mm噴嘴火焰噴射裝置。游標右鍵按下應該可以直接向前發射。內部的Gel Cartridges應該能夠從庫存中的任何地方提取煤泥。由於未發現煤泥的再生來源，目前的模型需要定期修改。
description.badge.name: 創造模式專屬物品,左鍵點擊一個怪物打開一個GUI，放置在這個介面中的物品可以稍後透過再次用徽章左鍵點擊來存取，並且在附屬的怪物被殺死時掉落。
description.backpack.name: 右鍵打開
description.alchemy_bag.name: 右鍵打開，只能儲存藥水
description.hookshot.name: 右鍵射擊抓鉤。一旦鉤子碰到方塊，你就會被拽過去。
description.longshot.name: 右鍵射擊抓鉤。一旦鉤子碰到方塊，你就會被拽過去。
description.moonlight.name: 刀刃上的銘文寫著「我的力量只能在月光下喚醒」
description.sunshine.name: 刀刃上的銘文寫著「我的力量只能在陽光下被喚醒」
description.attack_damage_at_night.name: 夜間攻擊傷害
description.attack_damage_at_day.name: 白天攻擊傷害
description.staff_vampiric.name: 當你握著這根棍子時，它會散發出暗能量。如果你把它移近耳朵，你就會聽到它的要求。它的叫法很簡單：「右擊我」，當你這樣做的時候，你會看到，它確實發射了一個拋射物。雖然傷害很小，但如果你把它放在正確的地方，它會在你被擊中時治癒你。
description.staff_wind.name: 不管這是做什麼的，現在還不起作用。 #TODO
description.staff_poison.name: 不管這是做什麼的，現在還不起作用。 #TODO

description.spiked_glove.name: With the claws of a beast, and the strength of your arm, these gloves shall lead you far from harm. While wielding two, enjoy the view, for walls no longer hinder you.
description.spear_diamond.name: 製作精良的武器，攻擊距離可比普通的劍更長。右擊效果：蓄力延長魚叉距離。
description.cursed_bone.name: 召喚的暴徒:
description.dummy_shield.name: 盾牌的大致形狀。不會保護你免受攻擊。當對應的地牢生成時，導出的假人持有這個，而不是持有其怪物類型的通常盾牌。
description.giant_spider_poison.name: This stuff is crazy corrosive! Definitely far too dangerous for you to work with, but maybe there's a toxin expert you can talk to about crafting with it.
description.feather_golden.name: Take up a feather, gild it in gold, take a great leap and believe in the powers of old. You won't be harmed, provided you're armed, with the feather of Gold. But use sparingly, my falling friend, if the feather breaks, your life may end.
description.scale_turtle.name: One of a few pieces of the Giant Tortoise's shell you managed to salvage. Its sheer strength is such that none of your tools can even chip it. Perhaps there's someone out there with stronger crafting tools than yours who you can convince to lend you a hand?
description.horn_bull.name: This horn is tough enough that you could probably make a great weapon with it if you knew how to craft with animal horns. Maybe there's a craftsman out there who's more experiened on the subject.
description.leather_bull.name: Very high quality leather. The right craftsman could probably use this to forge the most aerodynamic gear you've ever seen!
description.ball_slime.name: Amazing. Slime with regeneration powers. The fact that it always returns to the same shape makes it difficult to work with, but the right craftsman could probably use this to make some gear with health-manipulating abilities, and any weapons that use slime as ammo are going to get a lot out of this stuff.
description.bone_monking.name: Whatever primal energy made the Monking so much more powerful than his peers still clings to his bones. Perhaps the right craftsman would know how to work with such power?
description.leather_spider.name: The Giant Spider's hide still sticks to everything it touches. It's too gross for you to touch for a long period of time, but a craftsman who's more accustomed to such work can probably fashion this into something neat.
description.king_crown.name: Can be worn on its own, or combined with a helmet. Either way, you'll look as regal as you've always felt.
description.bubble_pistol.name: Undertech Commercial Turbo Dampener 33.6mm nozzle bubble explusion unit. A right-mouse press will expell a quick flurry of bubbles, large enough to capture a horse and drift upward. Bubbles are non-lethal, but can't say so much for the fall. Hold down Right Mouse Button for a steady stream.
description.bubble_rifle.name: Undertech Prototype advanced Turbo Dampener. Not for public access. Expells liquid faster and further than a traditional bubble gun, and holding the Right Mouse button lasts for longer. Unfortunately, reloading it is far slower.
description.path_tool.name: Sneak+Left Click an entity to apply the path to that entity.%sLeft Click an entity to copy the path of that entity.%sSneak+Right Click a block to add a new path node.%sRight Click a block to select an existing path node.%sSneak+Right Click air to clear the current path.
description.gui_merchant_edit_trade.igno: When checked the input does not have to be similar in terms of meta data. For example you set a diamond sword as input, it will also accept damaged diamond swords for it.
When checked the input does not have to be similar in terms of nbt data. For example you set a diamond sword as input, it will also accept enchanted diamond swords for it.
description.gui_merchant_edit_trade.repu: Reputation with the traders faction required to use this trade. Set it to "NONE" to not require any reputation.
description.gui_merchant_edit_trade.adva: Advancement required to use this trade. Specify an advancements resourcelocation (for example "minecraft:story/mine_stone) or leave it blank to not require any advancement.
description.gui_merchant_edit_trade.stoc: Check this to set that this trade has a stock count. This means that this trade has a limited use.
description.gui_merchant_edit_trade.rest: Amount of uses it will increase when it gets restocked. Every time you buy something, it will restock a different trade that is not maxed out.
description.gui_merchant_edit_trade.in_s: Current amount of uses the trade has.
description.gui_merchant_edit_trade.max_: Highest amount of uses the trade can have.
description.gui_button_trade.locked.name: Trade is not unlocked yet!
description.gui_button_trade.out_of_stoc: Out of stock! If possible buy something else, then maybe the trade will be in stock again.
